data.description:
Recently updated and freshly painted 4 bedroom with 1.5 baths and large yard. Near schools and local park. Easy access to highway and shopping.

Renter is responsible for all utilities. Pets considered on case-by-case basis with non-refundable deposit. No smoking inside the house.
